### Variables
###
GET http://localhost:8080/api/reserve-funds
###
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/reserve-funds
###
@userId = 1
@recipientId = 2

###
### Create Fund
###
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 1000.00,
  "currency": "XOF",
  "transactionType": "DEPOSIT",
  "description": "Initial deposit",
  "userId": {{userId}},
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

###

POST {{baseUrl}}/deposit?userId={{userId}}&amount=500.00&description=Additional+deposit
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Withdraw Funds
POST {{baseUrl}}/withdraw?userId={{userId}}&amount=200.00&description=Emergency+withdrawal
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Transfer Funds
POST {{baseUrl}}/transfer?fromUserId={{userId}}&toUserId={{recipientId}}&amount=100.00&description=Gift
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get Fund by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Fund by Reference (Replace with actual reference)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reference/REF-123456
Accept: application/json

###

### Get All Funds by User ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/{{userId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get All Funds by Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/status/ACTIVE
Accept: application/json

###

### Get All Funds
GET {{baseUrl}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Total Balance by User ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/{{userId}}/balance
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Total Active Balance (System wide)
GET {{baseUrl}}/balance/total
Accept: application/json

###

### Update Fund Status
PUT {{baseUrl}}/1/status?status=FROZEN
Accept: application/json

###

### Delete Fund (Cancel)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Transaction History
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/{{userId}}/history?startDate=2023-01-01T00:00:00&endDate=2025-12-31T23:59:59
Accept: application/json

###
